OL,3,CJury resumes deliberations in Sir
OL,4,CJeffrey Donaldson sex abuse trial
OL,6,FA jury in the sex offences trial of
OL,7,Fformer DUP leader Sir Jeffrey
OL,8,FDonaldson has resumed deliberations.
OL,10,FThe jury at Newry Crown Court is
OL,11,Fconsidering its verdict for a second
OL,12,Fday after deliberating for three hours
OL,13,Fand 10 minutes on Thursday.
OL,15,FThe 63-year-old former MP has pleaded
OL,16,Fnot guilty to 18 alleged offences.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
