OL,3,CJury resumes deliberations in Sir
OL,4,CJeffrey Donaldson sex abuse trial
OL,6,FThe charges include one count of rape
OL,7,Fand allegations of indecent assault
OL,8,Fand gross indecency, and span a period
OL,9,Fbetween 1985 and 2008 involving two
OL,10,Falleged victims.
OL,12,FComplainants A and B have both given
OL,13,Fevidence at the trial. Both women
OL,14,Fallege they were abused as children.
OL,16,FDonaldson spent two days giving
OL,17,Fevidence during the trial.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
