OL,3,CJury resumes deliberations in Sir
OL,4,CJeffrey Donaldson sex abuse trial
OL,6,FHis wife, Eleanor Donaldson, 60, from
OL,7,FDublinhill Road, Dromore, Co Down,
OL,8,Fdenies several charges of aiding and
OL,9,Fabetting her husband's alleged
OL,10,Foffending.
OL,12,FShe is facing a trial of the facts on
OL,13,Fmental health grounds.
OL,15,FThe trial of the facts will test the
OL,16,Fevidence in the case but cannot result
OL,17,Fin a criminal conviction.
OL,19,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,20,FITVX
